script.name: plugin.guilds.cabinmenu
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds'
if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input
else if $a.event == [MEvent.IsHidden] $obj.owner = $a.obj -> get owner race if $obj.owner == Player $tPassengers = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='loaded.passengers' if $tPassengers if size of table $tPassengers return [FALSE] end end end return [TRUE]
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Select] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] if $menu.id == 'cabin.menu' $tPassengers = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='loaded.passengers' if $tPassengers $passenger.data = $tPassengers[$selection] if $passenger.data START $a.obj ->open menu script: script=plugin.guilds.passenger.infomenu, value=$passenger.data end end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Finished]
end
* =============================================== return null
* =============================================== * =============================================== sub.BuildMenu: $menu = create custom menu array
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=100020 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$read.text
$tPassengers = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='loaded.passengers' if not $tPassengers $read.text = read text: page=[Input.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text else if not size of table $tPassengers $read.text = read text: page=[Input.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text else $sorted.array = sort table keys: table=$tPassengers $i = 0 $size = size of array $sorted.array while $i < $size $passenger.name = $sorted.array[$i] $passenger.data = $tPassengers[$passenger.name] inc $i =
$POS.TITLE = 25 $POS.DETAILS = 150
$cabin = $passenger.data['occupied'] gosub sub.GetCabin $text.cols = array alloc: size=2 $text = create custom menu string type icon: type=Space Suit $text = create custom menu column string, position=1 length=15 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[0] = $text $text = create custom menu column string, position=12 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$cabin $text.cols[1] = $text $ret = create menu return value: callback, value=$passenger.name add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.cols returnvalue=$ret
$text = 100030 $text.data = $passenger.data['race'] gosub sub.DisplayData
$text = 100010 $text.data = $passenger.name gosub sub.DisplayData
$text = 100013 $text.data = $passenger.data['travel.type'] $text.data = 100020 + $text.data $text.data = read text: page=$page.id id=$text.data gosub sub.DisplayData
$text = 100015 $text.data = $passenger.data['pay'] $text.data = convert number $text.data to string $text.data = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $text.data, [Text.Credits], null, null, null gosub sub.DisplayData
$text = 100018 $text.data = $passenger.data['xp'] $text.data = convert number $text.data to string gosub sub.DisplayData end
end
set menu option: $menu, icon=22
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=137 $input = create input: id='cabin.menu' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$a.obj callback=null endsub
* =============================================== * =============================================== sub.DisplayData: $text.cols = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=$text $text = sprintf: fmt='%s:', $read.text, null, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=$POS.TITLE length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[0] = $text $text = create custom menu column string, position=$POS.DETAILS length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text.data $text.cols[1] = $text add extra select line: menu=$menu, text=$text.cols endsub
* =============================================== * =============================================== sub.GetCabin: if $cabin == Budget Cabin (Occupied) $cabin = Budget Cabin else if $cabin == Executive Cabin (Occupied) $cabin = Executive Cabin else if $cabin == Family Cabin (Occupied) $cabin = Family Cabin else if $cabin == Luxury Cabin (Occupied) $cabin = Luxury Cabin else if $cabin == Standard Cabin (Occupied) $cabin = Standard Cabin end endsub
* =============================================== return null
